{"tid":1657861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大家有無諗過所有cctv片同相都可以係假嘅","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T09:58:52.000Z","uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bca165586b4527bb5a8a0479cca1e95c50e24c82","tid":1657861,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"開始有人話抄車<br />\n<br />\n但其實我地唔應該用佢放出黎嘅cctv黎做結論，<br />\n<br />\n因為係放出黎之前，<br />\n<br />\n警察或者校方都一定睇過，<br />\n<br />\n睇完咪將有問題嗰啲剪走，<br />\n<br />\n放得返出黎嘅咪就係睇完都無問題嗰啲，<br />\n<br />\n甚至可能係1014播段假片出黎都仲得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日傳出黎嘅，<br />\n<br />\n可能又係佢地執乾執淨先放出黎，<br />\n<br />\n又可能係所有野都係後期制作造出黎，<br />\n<br />\n所有野都係佢地放出黎，<br />\n<br />\n想我地看圖講故事，<br />\n<br />\n跟本就咩都証明唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n<br />\n我相信警察係一定有殺人，<br />\n<br />\n爭在點樣處理條屍，<br />\n<br />\n可能仲有啲係運左去中國，<br />\n<br />\n或者暗地裡處理左，<br />\n<br />\n處理唔到運唔走嗰啲，<br />\n<br />\n咪就係最近啲屍體發現案。"},{"pid":"2f1fcb4adfdb898ce7cd0e64b86fb0ca29ed1d14","tid":1657861,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"10096eae31954729b2d190628d462489b63430c1","tid":1657861,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"我唔會自殺"},{"pid":"a2185f7791ff4222b9609fc840d4fe3a3c5ce996","tid":1657861,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"利申 尻up 講下廢話"},{"pid":"8cfafa002b0484daeb607009efcf8eb0e900cbbe","tid":1657861,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70a4d3084cbbc335b8d9d4056dff1b937f5c1871","tid":1657861,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ac09f8d6d4116bcb5a